extendedInfo.description: The 2013 AICPA Conference on Tax Strategies for the High-Income Individual features an all-star cast of prominent tax experts and thought leaders sharing their timely insights, solutions, and personal experiences, focusing on the latest income and estate tax changes that may impact you and your high-income clients.App Keywords: aicpa, cpa2biz, Legislative Update, Individual Income Tax, Real Estate, Eric Solomon, Bob Jennings, John Connors, Stefan Tucker, Bryan Skarlatos, CPAs, attorneys, financial planners, estate planners, bank trust officers, insurance agents.
